item.title: CVE-2023-28365|2024-08-02T12:38:25.371Z -- ubiquiti%20inc. -- unifi%20network%20application
item.description: A backup file vulnerability found in UniFi applications (Version 7.3.83 and earlier) running on Linux operating systems allows application administrators to execute malicious commands on the host device being restored.
